Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:30.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:37.41,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:44.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:51.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:01:00.39,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.44,0:01:05.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:10.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:16.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:22.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚被神秘组织 『新亚特兰提斯』捉住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一名戴着面具 自称为『石像鬼』的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要求她交出『蔚蓝之水』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,面对男子的无情 不得不软化态度的娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告诉他东西在强的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一方面 强则与三人组一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,藏匿于杀人兵器 『巴别塔』的基座部分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.36,0:01:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,巴别塔的实验 就在他们面前进行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其威力足以轻松炸毁海上岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:02:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毁灭世界的恶魔之光 在此复苏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.01,0:02:06.53,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#08 娜蒂亚救出作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经查出发射地点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,方位SP03 RP40
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两舷全速 准备潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两舷全速 准备潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前部水槽注水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,引擎正常 连结推进器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全舰一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号 抵达目标深度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恢复至水平位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶的石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于让你完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人造山铜与巴别塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要有这座巴别塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要让世界再次臣服于我等亚特兰提斯跟前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可说是易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,塔内压力恢复至通常值
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发电及供电系统并无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,电子加速器并无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各记忆装置正常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全系统一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将电路复原\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,实验结束 将电路复原
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将电路复原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是倒霉透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还好吧 韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像有一团光芒发射出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对对 有光…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小子 那个女孩到哪去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小男孩 『蔚蓝之水』在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被那些家伙抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.53,0:04:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在巴别塔已经完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只剩尼莫的鹦鹉螺号 有待解决
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我将其击沉之前 你都是我重要的宾客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还真倔强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可别忘了 玛莉与那只狮子是死是活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全都得视你的态度而定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很快就会让你 见到你的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 就怕他已经成了 一具尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头 接下来该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 强 我们来帮你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是有句话说 『人人为我 我为人人』吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在离开这座岛之前 我们都是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们不会打娜蒂亚 『蔚蓝之水』的歪主意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样总行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那东西不见得 还会在娜蒂亚身上喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就从石像鬼手中抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然决定好了就事不宜迟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是潜水艇的出入口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为海潮退了 所以才露了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许有办法乘坐葛兰坦 从那个洞穴离开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰坦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 葛兰迪丝坦克 简称葛兰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:41.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我创造的万能战车
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唯一的缺点就是不具潜水机能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大姐头 你干嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么葛兰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明明帮它取了个好名字 就叫作『凯撒琳』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:07:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那部葛兰坦… 不 凯撒琳在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍微故障了 所以被我藏了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就藏在树林里 应该还没被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,马上就能修好对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你去把它开来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好是好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算是葛兰坦也挺麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座秘密基地四周都戒备森严
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要进出可没那么容易
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们说那是什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这点你们要想想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们是男人不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发电用的进水口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水是要做什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火力发电就是将水 变成水蒸气来转动涡轮发电
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 一旦把水拦住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就会停电！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.68,0:08:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看 这一件件的美术品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是由1万2千年前 古代亚特兰提斯人所创作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来他们不光是科学 就连艺术也都相当发达
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,凭那些愚蠢的生物 根本创作不出这样的雕刻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对你讲解艺术是否太艰深了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尚未发现那名男孩 目前仍持续搜索中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常抱歉 有三名俘虏脱逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊…也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然早了点 不过 我需要你的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你那男朋友的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切全都视你的态度而定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.21,0:09:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想起来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强·洛克·拉帝格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强·洛克·拉帝格 你听到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乖乖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是拯救娜蒂亚 以及你朋友的唯一手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重复一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强·洛克·拉帝格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乖乖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好卑鄙的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没时间了 动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.75,0:10:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在可没空让你沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？怎么可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这怎么…可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得到一套变装服饰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点都不来劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还要再搞一套来穿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢…谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 你这男孩还真会添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感觉如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可能会好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实我也不愿意 祭出这样的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但也不能继续浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望你能谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你快放了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:39.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那样对你可不划算 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时间一到 我就会将你们一一处决
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人数多点才能活得久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为你会是最后一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你根本不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能让你那么认为 真令我感到无比的光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.81,0:12:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不了多久锅炉就会过热
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,砰砰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强·洛克·拉帝格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再等你一个钟头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时你若不乖乖现身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有只小狮子 将会因此蒙主宠召
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,准备好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少年 强·洛克·拉帝格 主动现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真勇敢的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了爱是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎 强·洛克·拉帝格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 强 告诉我『蔚蓝之水』的下落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道娜蒂亚把它交给你保管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用它来交换这两名女孩的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个交易应该不算太坏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不想一说出口就没命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除非你撤下军队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:27.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放了娜蒂亚他们 否则一切免谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 『蔚蓝之水』在你身上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.27,0:14:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 骗了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然会被小孩子给唬到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了 既然要帮就帮到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:15:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说 这些家伙实在让人生厌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么 强 这样你可以告诉我了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快放了娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然你可要挨皮肉痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就难说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的射击可是一流的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不要试试？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的周围有强化玻陨石保护
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那把枪根本伤不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很聪明的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再重新问你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『蔚蓝之水』在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？发生什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发电厂遭人破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕 有同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手 想伤到自己人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Goodbye！Adios！再见！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快追\N是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.23,0:16:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,派出轨道人型坦克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不晓得你石像鬼有多伟大啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 只要本大爷握住方向盘 包你没戏唱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.05,0:17:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他平常都是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.18,0:17:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放我下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要跟本大爷硬碰硬是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来吧…看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样？ 让开…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少来碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要撞上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 再来一发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,湖 跳到湖里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,改为水上模式 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直接从那个洞口逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.21,0:18:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少来碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别再进行无谓的抵抗 把船停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,否则下次将直接命中贵船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,万事休矣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.64,0:19:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都来到这里了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？鹦鹉螺？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟然让尼莫入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,巴别塔 发射准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目标鹦鹉螺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.53,0:19:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是石像鬼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发电系统遭到破坏 目前输出功率不到3%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要能瞄准鹦鹉螺 将其破坏就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多亏有他们 让我们逃过了一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直接离开这座岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去把娜蒂亚放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼号没有回应
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是防护罩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有电路连接
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加压正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,输出功率上升至3.2%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.43,0:20:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瞄准锁定鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.46,0:20:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射前30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他打算使用巴别塔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再会了 尼莫 还有鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,急速潜航 动作快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发射前10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:09.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,9 8 7 6 5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,耗费了庞大预算 与岁月所兴建的基地竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟让尼莫得知机密比起来 这点损失根本不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.99,0:22:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.69,0:22:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,区区数名入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就导致基地毁灭 这该算是谁的责任？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就以死谢罪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愚蠢的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:22:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:22:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要将代为保管的东西还你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你 强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.77,0:23:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.51,0:23:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸好大家都平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有新亚特兰提斯与石像鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.57,0:23:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.98,0:23:54.78,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:24:02.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.93,0:24:07.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:12.30,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.37,0:24:20.71,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.24,0:24:31.42,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.49,0:24:40.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.30,0:24:44.50,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.57,0:24:49.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.21,0:24:58.44,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.59,0:25:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你救了我们 尼莫舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.66,0:25:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要叫我舰长 这艘船并不是军舰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.87,0:25:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我明白了 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.50,0:25:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我来为你介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.77,0:25:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们是我的朋友 娜蒂亚与玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.81,0:25:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及狮子大王
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.77,0:25:26.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.78,0:25:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『尼莫的秘密』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.98,0:25:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家要看喔
